snippet.title: XEV 9e Uses Advanced Noise Cancellation To Block All Sound From Outside The Vehicle ЁЯФК #automobile
snippet.description:
The Mahindra XEV 9e promises a cabin so quiet it feels like the outside world disappears.

Marketing claims suggest "advanced noise cancellation" that blocks all external sound.

In reality, the SUV doesn't use traditional active noise cancellation with microphones and counter-waves.

Instead, it relies on passive noise isolation with acoustic laminated glass and smart material choices.

A 16-speaker Harman Kardon system with A.R. Rahman-composed "sonic themes" enhances the experience.

The result is a refined, serene cabin built on solid engineering rather than electronic gimmicks.

What are your thoughts?
